One thing I'd verify before coding

Check whether your project already uses:

record DTOs or Lombok DTOs

Projections or direct entity fetching

LogBuilder.withField() method name (some teams use withKeyValue())


Search for an existing GET API in the same service and mirror the exact style. Consistency with the codebase is usually valued more than introducing a new pattern.

Also ask:

> If no subscription exists for the customer, should I return 200 with null body, 204 No Content, or 404 Not Found?



That answer affects the controller implementation.